  "description": "This dinner keeps the palate warm and savory while leaning on vegetables and lentils more than fat. Ragi Semiya Upma brings a distinct structure, seasoning pattern, and grain-legume balance to the table.",
  "preparation": "",
  "cooking_steps": [
    "Heat a wide pan on medium heat with oil. Add mustard, urad dal, curry leaves, and chilli and cook 45 seconds.",
    "Add onion and vegetable and saute 3 minutes until just tender.",
    "Add the sevai, salt, and 30 ml water and toss on low heat for 2 minutes.",
    "Finish with coconut, toss once, and serve immediately."
  ],
